cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image-based place recognition and proposes a new global image descriptor computed from semantic and topological information. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the proposed method can be used for robot navigation in natural environments. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques for image retrieval. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new method for image-based place recognition. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on text or document retrieval, but the proposed method can be seen as a form of content-based image retrieval.
